basicInfo.name: Yeonhee
basicInfo.flavor: Yeonhee found the Knights and returned to her world, only to discover that the war had already ended. However, when a new conflict arose soon after, she stepped forward to bring it to an end.

Normal Attack.desc:
Single Enemy
 - Deals damage equal to 100% of Magic Attack 1 time(s).
 - 40% chance to inflict Sleep. [Duration: 1 Turn(s)]
Skill Enhancement Effect
 - Increases Damage: To 130% of Magic Attack.
Transcend Lv.2 Effect
 - Changes Number of Targets: To 2 Enemies

Skill 1.name: Calamitous Gesture
Skill 1.desc:
3 Enemies
 - Deals damage equal to 43% of Magic Attack plus 6% of the target's Max HP 3 time(s). (HP-based damage limited to 100% of caster's Attack)
Skill Enhancement Effect
 - Increases Damage: To 51% of Magic Attack plus 7% of the target's Max HP.

Skill 2.name: Eternal Slumber
Skill 2.desc:
All Enemies
 - Deals Defense-Ignoring damage equal to 41% of Magic Attack 3 time(s).
 - 50% chance to inflict Sleep. [Duration: 2 Turn(s)]
Skill Enhancement Effect
 - Increases Damage: To 55% of Magic Attack.

Passive.name: Otherworldly Insight
Passive.desc:
All Allies
 - Grants Magic Attack Boost. [Always Active].
 - Self
 - Grants All Damage Nullification. [Ends After: Taking 3 Hit(s)]
 - Grants All Damage Nullification. [Ends After: Taking 4 Hit(s)]
Skill Enhancement Effect
 - Increases Effect: Magic Attack Boost to 25%.
 - Increases Stacks: All Damage Nullification ends after taking 4 hit(s).
Transcend Lv.6 Effect
 - Self
 - Adds Effect: 35% Magic Damage Boost. [Duration: 3 Turn(s)]

transcendence.transcend_7: Increases All Attack, Defense, and HP by 2%.

profile.likes: Warm cocoa, sleep, quiet, personal pillow, blankets, bed
profile.dislikes: Loud things, coffee, green tea, being awake, effortful tasks
profile.story: At the onset of the War of Destruction, Yeonhee destroyed all of the belligerent forces around her because they were interrupting her sleep. She was granted a seat on the Four Lords as a result. She only acted in her own interest — to secure a quiet place for her to sleep. But the people around her quickly came to regard her as their savior.

basicInfo.name: Yeonhee
basicInfo.flavor: Despite Yeonhee's efforts, the war raged on. Seeking a solution, she journeyed to the temple and received an that oracle revealed that knights from the Otherworld could end the conflict. Determined, she traveled to find them.
